bgm.name: 探索15(セキュリティホール)

parameters:
\n<Female>Hm? What? You're on an investigation...? Asking if I
recognize this man?

\n<Female>Could be a ghost, right? Maybe he wanted to see his wife's
face before passing on. The Mason couple were quite close,
after all.

\n<Female>Are you an adventurer? I haven't seen your face before. It's
better for you not to approach the residential area.
Unfamiliar faces are met with suspicion. You should stop
here.

\n<Female>If you're free, you might as well offer a prayer at the
church. There might be some kind of blessing for you. Not
that I would know.

\n<Female>Is it true that the sister was using necromancy? I can't
imagine such a good child doing that. It must be a nasty
rumor.

\n<Female>Right now, whether it was the sister who put it up or
someone else, we can't enter the church. With strange rumors
going around, it must be hard to protect oneself.

\n<Female>It seems like it was just a nasty rumor that the sister was
using necromancy. I'm glad the church is back to normal.

\n<Female>I wonder who spread such a rumor. They're the scum of the
earth. May they be cursed!

\n<Female>To think that the Sister was really using necromancy...
Well, I suspected that woman was shady from the start. So
much for her "mercy to all people."

\n<Female>She came here just because it was easy to get corpses. If
she likes dead bodies so much, she should just become one
herself.

"Storm Sect Drine Branch" - Bringing gentle breezes and the
saving flash of lightning even to the depths of the earth.
Entrust us with funerals and cemetery management as well.

A considerably powerful green barrier has been erected. It's
likely made with the power of wind magic. It seems it will
take some time to dispel...

A considerably powerful green barrier has been cast. It's
likely made with the power of wind magic. It seems it will
take time to dispel...
\n<Bearded Moja>Uhe... hehehehe...! O? O? Fufuhehe! Heh! Hehehehehe!!

They keep laughing to themselves... It's scary, so I should
stay away.

It's the ancestor! They seem to be sleeping comfortably...
Let's leave them be quietly.
